children.content: Key Orange flows = New Blue flows = Changed Black flows = existing
VocaLink provide headend to process authorisation requests from the ATM. Provide end of day and interim balance figures to ATM Service
Arrow hosts ATM Cash Management dashboard used by IMT. Provides Pouch and initial Cash on Hand data to ATM Service which then augments with data from VocaLink and Horizon to feed the dashboard.
CFS handles settlement with VocaLink and banks plus postmaster remuneration
Credence holds detailed ATM transactions and data from Horizon balance events. Used to support customer and branch queries
ATM Service is core service that processes data from VocaLink ad tracks branch reconciliation. Responsible for providing ATM and revised branch holding data to Arrow
